stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> CacheMiss: First request<br/>for this URL

    CacheMiss: Cache MISS
    note right of CacheMiss
        Edge has no copy.
        Fetch from origin.
    end note

    CacheMiss --> FetchOrigin: Forward to origin<br/>(or mid-tier)

    FetchOrigin: Fetch from Origin
    note right of FetchOrigin
        Origin responds with:
        - Content body
        - Cache-Control headers
        - ETag / Last-Modified
    end note

    FetchOrigin --> StoreInCache: Origin returns 200 OK<br/>with cacheable headers

    StoreInCache: Store in Cache
    note right of StoreInCache
        Cache stores:
        - Response body
        - Headers
        - TTL from s-maxage
        - ETag for revalidation
    end note

    StoreInCache --> Fresh: TTL timer starts

    Fresh: FRESH (Cache HIT)
    note right of Fresh
        Age < max-age/s-maxage
        Serve immediately.
        No origin contact.
    end note

    Fresh --> Fresh: More requests<br/>(served from cache)
    Fresh --> Stale: TTL expires<br/>(age > s-maxage)

    Stale: STALE
    note right of Stale
        Content past TTL.
        Behavior depends on
        Cache-Control directives.
    end note

    Stale --> ServeStaleRevalidate: stale-while-revalidate<br/>Serve stale, revalidate async
    Stale --> Revalidate: must-revalidate<br/>or no SWR directive
    Stale --> ServeStaleOnError: Origin returns 5xx<br/>+ stale-if-error set

    ServeStaleRevalidate: Serve Stale + Async Revalidate
    ServeStaleRevalidate --> Revalidate: Background revalidation

    Revalidate: Conditional Request
    note right of Revalidate
        If-None-Match: "etag"
        If-Modified-Since: date
    end note

    Revalidate --> Fresh: Origin returns 304<br/>Not Modified<br/>(TTL refreshed)
    Revalidate --> StoreInCache: Origin returns 200<br/>New content<br/>(replace cached copy)

    ServeStaleOnError: Serve Stale on Error
    note right of ServeStaleOnError
        Origin is down or 5xx.
        Serve stale content
        for up to N seconds.
    end note
    ServeStaleOnError --> Stale: Continue serving stale

    Fresh --> Purged: Explicit purge<br/>(API call)
    Stale --> Purged: Explicit purge

    Purged: PURGED / Evicted
    Purged --> CacheMiss: Next request<br/>triggers new fetch
